---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="Cookie Policy | DirectFlight.net" description="Cookie policy for DirectFlight.net — what cookies we use and how to control them." noindex={true}>
<section class="page-header"><div class="page-header-inner"><div class="page-eyebrow">📄 Legal</div><h1>Cookie Policy</h1><p>Last updated: March 26, 2026</p></div></section>
<div class="policy-wrap">
<div class="policy-meta">Questions? Email <a href="mailto:hello@directflight.net">hello@directflight.net</a></div>
<p>This Cookie Policy explains how DirectFlight.net uses cookies and similar tracking technologies. By continuing to use the Site, you consent to cookies as described here.</p>
<h2>What Are Cookies?</h2>
<p>Cookies are small text files placed on your device when you visit a website. They can be session cookies (deleted when you close your browser) or persistent cookies (stored until they expire). They can be set by us (first-party) or by our partners (third-party).</p>
<h2>Cookies We Use</h2>
<h3>Essential Cookies</h3>
<table>
<thead><tr><th>Cookie</th><th>Purpose</th><th>Duration</th></tr></thead>
<tbody>
<tr><td>cookie_consent</td><td>Stores your consent preference</td><td>12 months</td></tr>
<tr><td>theme</td><td>Remembers light/dark preference</td><td>12 months</td></tr>
</tbody>
</table>
<h3>Analytics Cookies (Google Analytics)</h3>
<table>
<thead><tr><th>Cookie</th><th>Purpose</th><th>Duration</th></tr></thead>
<tbody>
<tr><td>_ga</td><td>Distinguishes unique visitors</td><td>2 years</td></tr>
<tr><td>_ga_*</td><td>Persists session state</td><td>2 years</td></tr>
<tr><td>_gid</td><td>Distinguishes users within 24 hours</td><td>24 hours</td></tr>
</tbody>
</table>
<h3>Advertising Cookies (Google AdSense)</h3>
<table>
<thead><tr><th>Cookie</th><th>Purpose</th><th>Duration</th></tr></thead>
<tbody>
<tr><td>IDE</td><td>Records ad clicks for effectiveness tracking</td><td>13 months</td></tr>
<tr><td>__gads / __gpi</td><td>Ad impression registration and fraud prevention</td><td>13 months</td></tr>
</tbody>
</table>
<h3>Affiliate Tracking Cookies</h3>
<p>When you click affiliate links to Skyscanner, Expedia, Kayak, or other partners, those partners may set their own cookies (typically 30 days) to track referrals for commission attribution. These are governed by each partner's own privacy policy.</p>
<h2>How to Control Cookies</h2>
<p>You can block or delete cookies through your browser settings. Note that disabling essential cookies may affect site functionality. To opt out of personalized advertising, visit <a href="https://adssettings.google.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Google's Ads Settings</a> or the <a href="https://optout.aboutads.info" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Digital Advertising Alliance opt-out</a>.</p>
<h2>Changes</h2>
<p>We may update this policy from time to time. The "Last updated" date will reflect changes.</p>
<h2>Contact</h2>
<p>Email: <a href="mailto:hello@directflight.net">hello@directflight.net</a> · Jurisdiction: Alberta, Canada</p>
</div>
</BaseLayout>
